03:23.000 --> 03:32.000
If we talk about general methods of research, then they are divided into three groups.

03:32.000 --> 03:39.000
These are, first of all, empirical methods, that is, experimental research,

03:39.000 --> 03:45.000
methods that can be used both empirically and theoretically,

03:45.000 --> 03:49.000
