14:30.000 --> 14:36.000
To understand the processes that are taking place inside the team.

14:36.000 --> 14:45.000
And even sometimes not only inside the team, but inside the thinking processes.

14:45.000 --> 14:51.000
This is illustrated very well in the example of the Org.

14:51.000 --> 14:56.000
To understand the true feelings, thoughts and experiences of people.

14:56.000 --> 15:03.000
That is, the hidden layer can be seen only by the method of included observation.

15:03.000 --> 15:13.000
It is also important that almost all the collected data is useful in this study.

15:13.000 --> 15:23.000
