15:41.000 --> 15:43.000
There are also disadvantages.

15:43.000 --> 15:49.000
The first one is that it is a very long process.

15:49.000 --> 15:54.000
Especially when we talk about the last two.

15:54.000 --> 15:59.000
When people know that they are being observed.

16:00.000 --> 16:12.000
Another disadvantage is that conflict situations often arise within the framework of this method of study.

16:12.000 --> 16:18.000
