19:06.000 --> 19:12.000
Or, in principle, this phenomenon is observed in almost the entire company.

19:12.000 --> 19:22.000
In this case, the method of observation is supplemented by the method of interview.

19:22.000 --> 19:30.000
And once again, we return to the thesis that one method may not be good enough,

19:30.000 --> 19:39.000
but its disadvantages or limitations, to put it more correctly, can be fulfilled by another method.

19:39.000 --> 19:52.000
This is why qualitative research is difficult, although quantitative research is also not free from such issues.

19:52.000 --> 20:00.000
