26:01.000 --> 26:04.000
What should be noted?

26:04.000 --> 26:08.000
We are operating in two categories.

26:09.000 --> 26:14.000
This is an experimental group and a control group.

26:14.000 --> 26:16.000
Why?

26:16.000 --> 26:19.000
Why should there be an experimental group and a control group?

26:19.000 --> 26:26.000
An experimental group is the one that is affected by something,

26:26.000 --> 26:32.000
to see what response this effect will have.

26:32.000 --> 26:36.000
In any case, for an experimental group,

26:36.000 --> 26:48.000
the assessment of the quality or quantitative state of the experimental group is carried out before the start of the study and after.

26:48.000 --> 26:54.000
Sometimes immediately after and significantly after.

26:54.000 --> 26:56.000
What is the need of a control group?

26:56.000 --> 27:06.000
I think that for you it is not a discovery that people, participating in experiments, change their behavior.

27:06.000 --> 27:09.000
A fact known from medicine.

27:09.000 --> 27:16.000
If a person is given a candy and told that this is a pill that will reduce heart pain,

27:16.000 --> 27:18.000
it is called placebo,

27:18.000 --> 27:22.000
then indeed their heart will hurt less.

27:22.000 --> 27:28.000
Moreover, the more a person is affected by the influence of other people,

27:28.000 --> 27:30.000
psychologically dependent,

27:30.000 --> 27:32.000
the higher the effect will be.

27:32.000 --> 27:36.000
To level this influence,

27:36.000 --> 27:39.000
the person's awareness that he is participating in an experiment,

27:39.000 --> 27:41.000
a control group is required.

27:41.000 --> 27:48.000
In a control group, measurements or data collection can be carried out before the start of the experiment

27:48.000 --> 27:54.000
and after the experiment where we carry out the effect.

27:54.000 --> 28:02.000
Measurements and data collection can be carried out only after the experiment is over.

28:02.000 --> 28:12.000
Experiments can be carried out in social groups and in the business environment.

28:12.000 --> 28:17.000
Although this can be coupled with certain difficulties,

28:17.000 --> 28:23.000
