28:26.000 --> 28:31.000
The next method of empirical research is comparison.

28:31.000 --> 28:42.000
That is, you need to establish with this method the common thing that is inherent in two or several objects.

28:42.000 --> 28:46.000
I think that everyone knows this saying.

28:46.000 --> 28:50.000
Everything is known in comparison.

28:50.000 --> 28:55.000
But if we talk about the reliability of this method,

28:55.000 --> 29:05.000
