29:09.000 --> 29:15.000
between which there is a certain objective community.

29:15.000 --> 29:20.000
There is no point in comparing, say, an elephant and a fly.

29:20.000 --> 29:25.000
Although, what to choose for a unit of comparison?

29:25.000 --> 29:28.000
And the second is that for the identification of objects,

29:28.000 --> 29:38.000
the comparison should be carried out according to the most important objective significant signs.

29:38.000 --> 29:40.000
And not in general.

29:40.000 --> 29:49.000
It is also important to note that both quantitative and qualitative characteristics can be compared.

